TITLE: React Hooks for Koota ECS Integration
DESCRIPTION: Introduces React hooks for integrating Koota ECS with React components, including useQuery, useQueryFirst, and useWorld.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/koota/blob/main/packages/publish/README.md#2025-04-12_snippet_27

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const entities = useQuery(Position, Velocity);

return (
  <>
    {entities.map(entity => <View key={entity.id()} entity={entity} />)}
  </>
);

const player = useQueryFirst(Player, Position);

return player ? (
  <View entity={player} />
) : null;

const world = useWorld();

useEffect(() => {
    const entity = world.spawn()
    return => entity.destroy()
}, [])
```

