TITLE: Initializing World Provider in React
DESCRIPTION: Sets up a WorldProvider component to provide world context to child components. Creates a world instance and makes it available to all hooks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/koota/blob/main/packages/publish/README.md#2025-04-12_snippet_28

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
