TITLE: Querying and Updating Entity Data in Koota
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use queries to fetch entities sharing specific traits (archetypes) and batch update them efficiently. This example demonstrates updating position based on velocity.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/koota/blob/main/packages/publish/README.md#2025-04-12_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
// Run this in a loop
world.query(Position, Velocity).updateEach(([position, velocity]) => {
    position.x += velocity.x * delta;
    position.y += velocity.y * delta;
});
```

