TITLE: Creating Basic Entity Relationships in Koota
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create relationships between entities using the relation function, allowing entities to be connected and queried based on these connections.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/koota/blob/main/packages/publish/README.md#2025-04-12_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
const ChildOf = relation();

const parent = world.spawn();
const child = world.spawn(ChildOf(parent));

const entity = world.queryFirst(ChildOf(parent)); // Returns child
```

