TITLE: Using Added Query Modifier in Koota
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the Added modifier to track entities that have newly added specific traits since the last query, useful for responding to state changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/koota/blob/main/packages/publish/README.md#2025-04-12_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
import { createAdded } from 'koota';

const Added = createAdded();

// This query will return entities that have just added the Position trait
const newPositions = world.query(Added(Position));

// After running the query, the Added modifier is reset
```

